         xmlns:ns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
  <title>Compute bond lengths</title>

  <para>
  This modifier simply computes the length of each bond in the system and stores 
  it as bond property named <code>Length</code>. 
  You can use this in conjuncion with the <link linkend="particles.modifiers.color_coding">Color Coding</link>
  modifier to color bonds according to their length.
  </para>
  
</section>
